%% ============================================================
%% Ciclo de vida de uma ResearchNodeConnection no IRIS
%% Referenciado em: cap-experimentos-resultados.tex (4.3.3.4)
%% Label: fig:IRISEstadosConexao
%% ============================================================
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> UNKNOWN: POST /api/node/NewConnection

    UNKNOWN --> PENDING: Submeter para aprovacao

    PENDING --> AUTHORIZED: POST /api/node/{id}/approve
    PENDING --> REVOKED: POST /api/node/{id}/reject

    AUTHORIZED --> REVOKED: Revogar (admin local)
    REVOKED --> AUTHORIZED: Reaprovar

    AUTHORIZED --> AUTHORIZED: POST /api/sync/pull<br/>(atualiza lastSyncedAt)

    note right of UNKNOWN
        Conexao recem-criada
        localmente. Aguarda
        submissao.
    end note

    note right of PENDING
        Visivel na aba Requests
        do NodeConnectionsScreen.
        Aguarda decisao do admin.
    end note

    note right of AUTHORIZED
        Sincronizacao permitida apenas
        se NodeAccessLevel for
        READ_WRITE ou ADMIN.
    end note

    note right of REVOKED
        Conexao bloqueada;
        nao pode sincronizar.
    end note
